data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE, NAME from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, FULL_TIME_EQVLNT from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD' and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadOfficeOfficeStaffing
data.value: select * from ( select T1.OFFICE_ID, T1.COG_TYPE_CODE, T1.COG_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T1 where T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and exists ( select * from CKT_CSE_ORG_RELATN T3 where T1.COG_TYPE_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_TYPE and T1.COG_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_CODE and T3.REASON_CODE = 'JC' and @cogChildType = T3.COG_CHILD_TYPE and @cogChildCode = T3.COG_CHILD_CODE ) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) YEAR_MONTH, F_T_E, OFF_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFFC_STAFFING where S1.OFFICE_ID = OFF_GENERATED_ID and YEAR_MONTH = @yearMonth ) S2

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority35
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, FULL_TIME_EQVLNT = @fullTimeEqvlnt where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
